title: Sal Solo Heart & Soul The Remixes
description:
Sal Solo 12" remixes of his first solo album

Originally a 5 track I added 2 other 12" singles from vinyl

A very rare extended remix cassette now LONG DELETED  

this was the second side of the original 1985 cassette only release.

San Damiano- vinyl
Music & You- vinyl
Heartbeat-cassette
Poland-cassette
Contact-cassette
Go Now-cassette
Forever Be-cassette

I offered this to Cherry Red records for the remaster of heart & Soul- they werent interested
